{"tid":800181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【五毛狗衝】港澳台居民將可申領支那居住證　北京市公安局公布樣式","createTime":"2018-08-30T16:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T05:39:05.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5cd52366f1f3194c48ec2581105adc3fd8c199c2","tid":800181,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1415465_1_L_20180830232013.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1415465_1_L_20180830232013.jpg&h=2561e9ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港澳台居民9月1日起，可到支那各地公安機關申領支那居住證，北京市公安局晚上率先公布居住證的樣式，與現行支那居民身分證樣式相似。<br />\n<br />\n證件的正面有長城作為背景，國徽位於證件左上角，國徽右側寫上「支那人民共和國港澳居民居住證」，或者「支那人民共和國台灣居民居住證」，並印有簽發機關名稱、有效期限，以及持有人來往支那的通行證號碼。<br />\n<br />\n證件背面則載有持證人的彩色照片、姓名、性別、出生日期、住址和公民身分號碼。<br />\n<br />\n按照規定，港澳台居民在支那居住半年以上，有合法穩定就業、住所、連續就讀，這三項條件的其中一項，便可以申領居住證。"},{"pid":"00f55a6a30f673a327a01e3064bfa28f9af9cedc","tid":800181,"uid":156652,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:01:14.000Z","msg":"要交稅不了"},{"pid":"8602538db472508bf4e4fee1a3ff25fa6018361b","tid":800181,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:02:14.000Z","msg":"五毛終於可以做二等支那人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2591b6bcffc6acb9066804eb2e856f55a6b8de4","tid":800181,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:05:44.000Z","msg":"五毛終於可以做 99.99% 支那人啦<br />\n<br />\n我等睇五毛 POST 二等支那證張相寸 BNO  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180830/s00004/71a2c766eb557787df7a7e513f6c9d83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180830%2Fs00004%2F71a2c766eb557787df7a7e513f6c9d83.jpg&h=298a9ce4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a53885bbdce9a491e2451caaf2773a67021ad2d","tid":800181,"uid":29606,"like